      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length studio group portrait: An elderly woman in a dark town dress is sitting between two younger women in light-coloured urban dresses. The latter are also sitting on chairs. One of them is leaning on a small light-coloured table on which a couple of flowers have been placed. A woman in a town dress is standing behind the table, and a young man wearing a light-coloured uniform is standing behind the two women sitting on the left. A painted canvas backdrop is creating the illusion of the scene being set in a lounge.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Krastina Batsarova-Zlatoustova (1860 - 1942), a teacher, with her children Bogdana, Maria, Matey and Ekaterina.</ab>
